query:
SELECT t.tabNumber, t.tabTitle, t.backgroundType, t.backgroundValue, d.slug 
FROM tabs_content t 
JOIN documents d ON t.documentId = d.id 
WHERE d.slug = 'busplan_2026_01' AND t.tabNumber = 7 
LIMIT 1;
